WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
♪To the horizon's call♪

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
♪Put every twist behind you♪

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
♪Drift leisurely through time♪

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
♪Make headway against the wind♪

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
♪Let mountains bow to your pace♪

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
♪Let your nature burst free♪

01:30.240 --> 01:34.490
=The First Jasmine=

01:35.388 --> 01:37.808
=Episode 36=

01:47.376 --> 01:49.057
Your Highness, your bed is made.

01:52.217 --> 01:54.137
It's fine to throw away the rouge,

01:54.417 --> 01:56.656
but the bedding sets
were perfectly good.

01:56.656 --> 01:58.816
What exactly is Nanny Xu trying to do?

01:59.256 --> 02:00.376
Is His Highness back?

02:00.617 --> 02:01.456
Yes.

02:15.576 --> 02:16.217
Yao,

02:16.497 --> 02:17.576
are you in there?

02:19.136 --> 02:19.937
Yes, I am.

02:25.057 --> 02:26.256
Why is the door locked?

02:27.457 --> 02:28.937
I'm fine. You may leave.

02:30.136 --> 02:31.376
You don't sound well.

02:31.497 --> 02:32.696
Did you catch a cold?

02:35.696 --> 02:38.096
You may leave,
and I'll be there in a while.

03:20.017 --> 03:22.057
Why did you lock the door
while you're reading?

03:26.976 --> 03:28.057
And without lamplight?

03:32.976 --> 03:33.777
It's so hot.

03:34.217 --> 03:35.136
Let me feel your pulse.

03:35.136 --> 03:35.937
No, no need.

03:35.937 --> 03:37.177
I'll go have some water.

03:52.017 --> 03:52.937
Aphrodisiac incense?

03:53.897 --> 03:54.897
Who gave it to you?

03:57.617 --> 03:59.457
You've been married for almost a year.

03:59.656 --> 04:01.536
You and Yao are in your prime.

04:01.536 --> 04:03.017
Aren't you eager to have a child?

04:03.816 --> 04:04.696
Ms. Wen?

04:06.416 --> 04:08.136
I only took a sip, so it's no big deal.

04:08.656 --> 04:09.696
You may leave.

04:23.977 --> 04:24.776
Please.

04:26.016 --> 04:27.256
We're husband and wife.

04:28.057 --> 04:29.737
We can talk it out tomorrow.

04:48.297 --> 04:49.937
This swallow's nest is rare.

04:50.336 --> 04:52.177
Steam it and send it to Li later.

04:53.057 --> 04:53.857
My Lady,

04:54.057 --> 04:56.057
I have already prepared it.

04:56.776 --> 04:59.376
And I've also given the nutrition recipe
to the cook.

04:59.376 --> 05:01.376
The cook will follow the recipe

05:01.376 --> 05:02.776
to make nutritious food.

05:02.776 --> 05:04.937
Don't worry, my lady.

05:08.057 --> 05:08.857
Your Highness.

05:18.896 --> 05:20.336
Why did you do this?

05:24.857 --> 05:26.216
You ask me?

05:27.336 --> 05:29.097
Yao, you should know why.

05:34.016 --> 05:35.376
You are going to Suixue Pass.

05:35.737 --> 05:36.696
I cannot stop you.

05:37.336 --> 05:39.576
You want to serve the court
and protect the country.

05:39.896 --> 05:42.497
That's your righteousness,
and who dares to stop you?

05:44.097 --> 05:45.376
But before you leave,

05:46.216 --> 05:48.776
you must have a child with Li.

05:50.216 --> 05:51.376
Li is still young.

05:52.657 --> 05:54.576
Indeed, she is.

05:55.376 --> 05:57.617
Nobody knows what will happen to you
on the battlefield.

05:59.016 --> 06:00.896
She has no family left.

06:01.336 --> 06:03.136
And Lishan Academy is also gone.

06:03.136 --> 06:04.297
She has no child now.

06:05.576 --> 06:06.376
Well,

06:07.776 --> 06:09.417
what if something happens to you?

06:10.057 --> 06:12.136
How is she supposed to live alone?

06:13.497 --> 06:14.617
I didn't do that

06:15.097 --> 06:16.657
for your Mo family.

06:17.977 --> 06:19.297
I did it for Li.

06:20.256 --> 06:21.937
As long as you and Li have a child,

06:22.216 --> 06:24.937
Li and I can raise the child together
and move on.

06:25.336 --> 06:27.896
And you can achieve your ambitions
without any worries.

06:29.297 --> 06:30.696
You brought Li down the mountain

06:31.737 --> 06:33.336
precisely for this day, didn't you?

06:50.417 --> 06:51.216
Yao.

06:56.016 --> 06:57.297
Have you talked with Ms. Wen?

06:58.136 --> 06:59.016
You already know?

07:00.097 --> 07:01.696
Ms. Wen is not an unreasonable person.

07:03.097 --> 07:04.256
Given what she did

07:04.376 --> 07:06.617
and your state after Gongshu Yang left

07:06.617 --> 07:07.576
the other day,

07:08.297 --> 07:09.937
it's not hard to guess what happened.

07:09.937 --> 07:11.097
When are you going to leave?

07:12.896 --> 07:14.216
I haven't decided yet.

07:15.617 --> 07:17.857
Commander Xiong Yisong was murdered,

07:18.057 --> 07:20.496
so the deputy is in charge for now.

07:21.737 --> 07:23.816
His Majesty and Gongshu Yang
both want me to go.

07:24.216 --> 07:24.977
But I...

07:24.977 --> 07:25.776
Yao,

07:26.696 --> 07:28.376
do you know why I fell ill

07:28.737 --> 07:30.376
when I was on Lishan Mountain?

07:35.016 --> 07:36.537
That's because I wanted to survive.

07:38.136 --> 07:39.737
I was too young then,

07:40.336 --> 07:42.216
unable to cope with that situation.

07:42.937 --> 07:44.937
That's why I fell ill.

07:45.937 --> 07:47.097
I was saving myself.

07:49.617 --> 07:51.177
Finally, I survived a hard time.

07:51.737 --> 07:53.136
So, what else is there to fear?

07:55.097 --> 07:56.417
Ms. Wen is worried about me,

07:57.057 --> 07:58.497
and you should understand.

07:59.376 --> 08:02.177
Besides, there is no war at Suixue Pass.

08:02.537 --> 08:03.576
If you go there,

08:03.576 --> 08:06.177
you'll just garrison the frontier
and train troops.

08:06.776 --> 08:09.696
You're in a high, powerful position,
so what is there to worry about?

08:10.737 --> 08:12.576
I'll write to you when I miss you.

08:13.097 --> 08:15.896
If I miss you too much, I'll go see you.

08:18.297 --> 08:20.737
Suixue Pass is far away.
How will you go?

08:22.657 --> 08:23.617
On horseback.

08:23.816 --> 08:25.456
I've been there. Remember?

08:26.256 --> 08:27.057
I remember.

08:27.937 --> 08:29.657
You were almost caught by bandits.

08:30.097 --> 08:31.617
They can't catch me now.

08:31.617 --> 08:33.696
I am as formidable as Master Zhu now.

08:47.616 --> 08:48.616
Thank you, Li.

09:04.616 --> 09:05.496
These people

09:05.696 --> 09:07.417
couldn't name a candidate when asked to.

09:08.017 --> 09:09.937
But after Gongshu Yang
proposed Prince Ding,

09:09.976 --> 09:11.456
they all submitted memorials together

09:11.537 --> 09:14.096
advising me not to send Prince Ding
to Suixue Pass.

09:16.777 --> 09:17.777
Calm down, Your Majesty.

09:18.777 --> 09:20.696
Prince Ding is familiar
with the frontier

09:20.696 --> 09:22.137
and capable of leading troops.

09:22.256 --> 09:24.336
He is the ideal candidate
to take over as commander.

09:24.336 --> 09:25.137
Your Majesty,

09:25.657 --> 09:26.616
just ignore opposition.

09:29.456 --> 09:30.456
What about Duke Hua?

09:31.856 --> 09:33.328
Duke Hua is old.

09:33.856 --> 09:35.344
He is almost retired

09:35.344 --> 09:37.137
and rarely meddles in court politics.

09:37.576 --> 09:38.856
When I visited him yesterday,

09:39.336 --> 09:41.777
his old injury had recurred
due to the continuous rain.

09:42.137 --> 09:44.417
He was tormented and looked miserable.

09:45.096 --> 09:47.257
He is indeed not the best candidate.

09:53.017 --> 09:53.657
Your Majesty,

09:53.976 --> 09:55.897
allow me to speak bluntly.

09:56.537 --> 09:58.336
In terms of the ability to fight,

09:58.336 --> 10:00.336
Prince Ding is the best in our nation.

10:00.696 --> 10:02.657
But when it comes to
guarding Suixue Pass,

10:02.736 --> 10:03.777
holding military power,

10:03.777 --> 10:06.377
deterring Cangbei,
and commanding the army,

10:06.377 --> 10:08.616
he is absolutely not the right person.

10:10.297 --> 10:11.096
Why not?

10:12.137 --> 10:12.777
That is

10:13.096 --> 10:15.297
because the court once broke his heart.

10:15.976 --> 10:18.377
Although Mo Xiuwen's death was caused
by Marquis Muyang,

10:18.696 --> 10:20.696
who was behind it?

10:21.336 --> 10:22.137
Back then,

10:22.537 --> 10:24.297
as Mo Xiuwen led troops to the capital,

10:24.576 --> 10:26.177
the Eastern Palace caught fire,

10:26.537 --> 10:27.696
and the Crown Prince died.

10:27.696 --> 10:29.616
Otherwise, what would have happened?

10:29.777 --> 10:30.537
Li Duo,

10:31.216 --> 10:32.616
without any evidence,

10:32.777 --> 10:34.417
how can you maliciously speculate?

10:34.736 --> 10:36.137
Prince Ding is utterly loyal.

10:36.137 --> 10:37.137
It's clear to all.

10:37.137 --> 10:38.976
Generally, military power
is imperial power.

10:41.657 --> 10:43.336
I certainly hope

10:43.496 --> 10:44.937
Prince Ding is absolutely good.

10:45.257 --> 10:47.216
I hope that he remains loyal

10:47.216 --> 10:49.417
to Dachu and Your Majesty
after being wronged for years.

10:49.736 --> 10:51.937
I do not wish to suspect a good general.

10:52.496 --> 10:55.017
I only want to remind Your Majesty

10:55.777 --> 10:59.057
that people could change.

11:00.017 --> 11:01.017
We cannot gamble.

11:03.537 --> 11:04.537
Do you have anyone else

11:05.137 --> 11:06.057
in mind?

11:09.297 --> 11:10.096
Your Majesty,

11:10.576 --> 11:11.377
I've learned

11:11.496 --> 11:13.057
military strategy since childhood.

11:13.057 --> 11:14.937
I once served
as General of the Left Army,

11:15.297 --> 11:17.456
wrote the "Frontier Farming Strategy,"

11:17.937 --> 11:19.657
and led troops in military drills.

11:19.976 --> 11:22.096
I believe I'm able to lead troops.

11:23.336 --> 11:24.216
Li Duo,

11:24.657 --> 11:25.976
what do you mean by that?

11:28.177 --> 11:29.777
I request

11:30.017 --> 11:32.297
to let me guard Suixue Pass.

11:41.177 --> 11:42.657
Li Duo is going to Suixue Pass?

11:43.137 --> 11:43.937
Yes.

11:44.177 --> 11:46.856
The edict has been issued,
and Li Duo will leave for it tomorrow.

12:02.696 --> 12:04.297
Suixue Pass is a frontier fortress

12:04.777 --> 12:06.177
and Dachu's northern gateway.

12:06.537 --> 12:08.017
With Suixue Pass standing,

12:08.017 --> 12:10.297
if Cangbei invades,
they must cross the mountains

12:10.297 --> 12:11.777
and camp along the way.

12:12.336 --> 12:13.576
Without Suixue Pass,

12:14.137 --> 12:15.417
if Cangbei intends to invade,

12:15.657 --> 12:18.017
they only need to cross the Hukou Plain
and head south

12:18.336 --> 12:20.096
to reach the capital directly.

12:21.736 --> 12:22.576
I know.

12:23.177 --> 12:24.216
Since Your Majesty knows,

12:24.696 --> 12:26.696
why send Li Duo to Suixue Pass?

12:27.057 --> 12:28.856
He has never been on the battlefield.

12:29.657 --> 12:32.576
Can he guard such an important fortress
like Suixue Pass?

12:34.257 --> 12:35.057
I don't believe

12:35.937 --> 12:36.976
he can do it.

12:37.816 --> 12:40.216
So, who do you think I should send?

12:40.856 --> 12:42.816
My clan has guarded Suixue Pass

12:43.017 --> 12:44.297
for generations.

12:44.616 --> 12:46.216
If my brother hadn't been framed...

12:46.216 --> 12:46.976
Xiuyao.

12:55.736 --> 12:57.777
Your Majesty,
are you questioning my loyalty?

13:01.537 --> 13:04.496
I just don't want you to suffer
on the frontier anymore.

13:05.456 --> 13:06.576
Life is harsh there.

13:07.137 --> 13:08.816
Your leg injury has just healed.

13:08.816 --> 13:10.496
What if your old injury is back?

13:10.937 --> 13:13.137
You've only been married for a year
with no children.

13:13.937 --> 13:15.417
Suixue Pass

13:15.417 --> 13:16.777
is a dangerous place.

13:17.137 --> 13:18.456
If something happens to you,

13:18.736 --> 13:20.736
how will I explain
to your wife and Ms. Wen?

13:21.537 --> 13:23.177
Li Duo has never been
on the battlefield,

13:23.696 --> 13:25.777
but he is experienced
in assessing the situation

13:25.777 --> 13:26.897
and managing subordinates.

13:27.456 --> 13:30.336
I am sending him, only hoping
that he can manage people well

13:30.616 --> 13:32.096
and keep the frontier peaceful.

13:32.336 --> 13:34.057
I don't expect him to go into battle

13:34.177 --> 13:35.696
and win.

13:37.496 --> 13:38.297
Xiuyao.

13:38.657 --> 13:40.137
I am no longer a child.

13:40.417 --> 13:42.216
I can tell
if outsiders want to sow discord

13:42.216 --> 13:43.336
between us.

13:43.736 --> 13:46.616
But I have my own reasons
to make this decision.

13:47.856 --> 13:48.696
Li Duo

13:48.696 --> 13:50.537
has been loyal to me these years.

13:51.096 --> 13:52.616
Since he requested it,

13:53.137 --> 13:54.417
why not give him a chance?

14:02.336 --> 14:03.696
Military power is a huge thing.

14:05.057 --> 14:06.537
If Your Majesty trusts him,

14:07.937 --> 14:08.736
it's fine.

14:09.496 --> 14:11.897
Gao Wenhuan will go with him
as the army supervisor.

14:14.537 --> 14:17.297
Rest assured,
there won't be any trouble.

14:23.216 --> 14:27.024
(Prince Ding's Mansion)

14:34.616 --> 14:35.816
Jin just told me

14:36.057 --> 14:38.616
that His Majesty won't send you
to Suixue Pass.

14:44.496 --> 14:45.576
Aren't you happy?

14:47.537 --> 14:49.137
I just feel like something is off.

14:50.216 --> 14:50.937
How so?

14:51.297 --> 14:52.137
I don't know.

14:52.897 --> 14:54.336
I just feel uneasy.

14:56.736 --> 14:57.777
The edict has been issued.

14:58.257 --> 15:00.456
It means His Majesty
has made up his mind.

15:00.856 --> 15:02.777
For now, we can only wait and see.

15:09.456 --> 15:10.537
Look on the bright side.

15:11.096 --> 15:12.816
You can stay and keep me company.

15:31.137 --> 15:31.937
Mingyue,

15:32.336 --> 15:33.417
are we leaving today?

15:35.336 --> 15:36.456
They made their move.

15:36.856 --> 15:38.736
The guards will
strengthen their patrols.

15:38.937 --> 15:40.456
They killed Xiong Yisong.

15:41.336 --> 15:42.537
What are they up to?

15:43.736 --> 15:44.897
Are they going to fight?

15:44.976 --> 15:46.017
Not so fast.

15:46.496 --> 15:48.057
When their man takes over,

15:48.657 --> 15:49.897
they will start a fight.

15:50.216 --> 15:52.657
But for now, they will definitely hide.

15:53.257 --> 15:55.257
So even if they find us missing,

15:55.257 --> 15:56.616
they won't act rashly.

15:57.377 --> 16:00.177
It's just a bit difficult
to leave the city now.

16:03.216 --> 16:03.907
Hyah!

16:04.368 --> 16:04.976
Hyah!

16:05.840 --> 16:06.511
Hyah!

16:07.856 --> 16:08.464
Hyah!

16:16.616 --> 16:17.417
Their men.

16:19.496 --> 16:20.336
Eat your food.

16:46.736 --> 16:47.616
Where is Han Mingyue?

16:49.137 --> 16:50.017
He went

16:51.696 --> 16:53.257
on a mission.

16:53.456 --> 16:54.336
A mission?

16:54.736 --> 16:55.777
How come I didn't know?

17:57.097 --> 17:57.897
Your Highness.

17:58.817 --> 18:00.536
What mission did Han Mingyue go on?

18:00.617 --> 18:01.337
Didn't you say

18:01.337 --> 18:03.177
we would do nothing
before Li Duo takes over?

18:03.536 --> 18:04.857
He hasn't been back all night.

18:04.857 --> 18:06.937
Could something have happened?

18:09.296 --> 18:10.097
Your Highness.

18:46.657 --> 18:48.536
Mingyue, how did it go?

18:52.319 --> 18:52.912
(Travel Pass)

18:55.456 --> 18:56.617
Where did you get this?

18:57.177 --> 18:57.976
It's fake.

18:58.897 --> 19:00.417
Be careful when leaving the city.

19:03.417 --> 19:05.056
With so many patrolling guards now,

19:05.817 --> 19:07.216
will we get into trouble?

19:08.097 --> 19:11.056
Since we've decided,
let's bet our lives on it.

19:11.536 --> 19:12.056
Okay.

19:12.536 --> 19:15.177
With you, I'm not afraid of anything.

19:20.880 --> 19:24.720
(Cloth Shop)

19:28.216 --> 19:29.137
Master,

19:30.337 --> 19:31.736
something happened at Suixue Pass.

19:32.137 --> 19:34.056
Do we really have to go to Cangbei?

19:34.897 --> 19:36.137
What if something happens?

19:36.897 --> 19:38.256
We've asked around for days,

19:38.657 --> 19:41.417
but we still don't know
what Cangbei will do with Su Zuidie.

19:43.296 --> 19:45.256
She killed their ruler's sister.

19:45.976 --> 19:47.776
She should be publicly executed.

19:49.177 --> 19:52.137
Maybe Cangbei
makes a different decision.

19:52.536 --> 19:54.056
Maybe she hasn't been executed yet.

19:55.496 --> 19:57.256
If so, we should go and find out.

19:58.016 --> 19:59.897
Only then can Lingyun rest in peace.

20:02.937 --> 20:04.776
Eat your food,
and then we'll hit the road.

20:05.097 --> 20:05.736
Okay.

20:46.937 --> 20:48.137
Are you leaving?

20:54.097 --> 20:54.976
Answer me.

20:56.897 --> 20:57.696
Zuidie,

20:58.456 --> 20:59.617
we can leave together.

21:02.617 --> 21:03.417
Why?

21:04.577 --> 21:05.617
Why are you leaving?

21:06.817 --> 21:08.736
Have you forgotten our revenge?

21:09.736 --> 21:12.256
Have you forgotten
what we've been through together?

21:12.256 --> 21:14.256
How many more times
are you going to bring it up?

21:14.897 --> 21:16.417
You only saved me once.

21:16.417 --> 21:19.337
My brother saved you so many times.
Isn't that enough?

21:23.097 --> 21:23.776
Mingyue.

21:24.577 --> 21:25.177
Let's go.

21:27.377 --> 21:28.216
Tell me.

21:29.056 --> 21:30.496
Are you really leaving?

21:31.857 --> 21:32.657
Yes.

21:33.377 --> 21:34.177
I'm leaving.

21:37.536 --> 21:38.377
Fine.

21:39.857 --> 21:40.696
Then leave.

21:45.696 --> 21:48.657
As long as you can get out alive.

21:59.577 --> 22:00.617
Su Zuidie,

22:01.216 --> 22:02.417
you lunatic!

22:03.296 --> 22:04.256
Did you hear that?

22:04.256 --> 22:05.377
What?

22:56.657 --> 22:57.577
Mingyue!

22:57.776 --> 22:58.696
Han Mingxi!

23:20.976 --> 23:21.857
Su Zuidie!

23:22.016 --> 23:23.216
I'll kill you!

23:35.817 --> 23:37.456
This is for Lingyun.

23:59.617 --> 24:00.536
Ruyi!

24:10.016 --> 24:10.776
Master!

24:10.976 --> 24:12.617
Kill her!

24:21.976 --> 24:22.897
This stab

24:23.696 --> 24:24.897
is for Dachu.

24:34.896 --> 24:35.590
Ruyi.

24:36.216 --> 24:37.016
Ruyi!

24:38.320 --> 24:39.016
Ruyi.

24:39.016 --> 24:40.256
Ruyi!

24:50.016 --> 24:50.817
Mingyue.

24:51.776 --> 24:52.577
Mingyue!

24:53.296 --> 24:54.097
Mingxi.

24:54.097 --> 24:54.897
Go!

24:55.177 --> 24:56.377
They will come again.

24:56.377 --> 24:57.056
You promised

24:57.657 --> 24:59.056
you would definitely take me away.

25:02.097 --> 25:02.897
Mingxi,

25:03.417 --> 25:04.417
listen to me.

25:05.056 --> 25:06.976
Go live the life you want.

25:17.417 --> 25:18.097
Mingyue.

25:19.736 --> 25:20.912
Mingyue!

25:22.016 --> 25:23.280
Mingyue!

25:26.507 --> 25:38.696
(Tomb of Han Mingyue, Tomb of Ruyi)

25:38.696 --> 25:40.736
It was my brother
who saved that bad woman.

25:42.897 --> 25:44.177
I'm sorry.

25:45.776 --> 25:47.137
Your brother has paid the price.

25:49.337 --> 25:51.177
I've avenged Lingyun's death.

25:54.456 --> 25:55.776
It will pass soon.

26:02.096 --> 26:04.944
(Tomb of Han Mingyue)

26:07.417 --> 26:08.377
Rest for two days,

26:09.177 --> 26:10.417
and then return together.

26:14.857 --> 26:16.137
I want to stay with my brother

26:17.776 --> 26:18.577
for a few days.

26:20.137 --> 26:21.496
Don't forget your brother's words.

26:23.577 --> 26:25.337
Go live the life you want.

26:40.256 --> 26:41.536
Your brother and Su Zuidie

26:42.897 --> 26:43.937
worked for the same guy.

26:45.056 --> 26:46.016
Who exactly is it?

26:49.577 --> 26:51.016
It's Mo Jingli.

26:52.736 --> 26:54.417
They killed Xiong Yisong.

26:55.937 --> 26:57.617
Their man replaced Xiong Yisong's place.

26:58.256 --> 26:59.976
Once the new replacement arrives,

27:00.456 --> 27:02.417
I'm afraid something big will happen.

27:06.296 --> 27:08.417
Where did you go this morning?
You came back so late.

27:11.177 --> 27:12.736
I went to Qingfeng Mingyue Tower.

27:14.577 --> 27:16.456
After Feng Zhiyao left the capital,

27:16.456 --> 27:17.577
I got no news from him.

27:17.976 --> 27:18.936
I'm a bit worried.

27:19.280 --> 27:21.200
So, I sent someone
to his hometown to inquire.

27:23.456 --> 27:24.857
The death of Princess Lingyun

27:24.857 --> 27:26.417
was a heavy blow to him.

27:26.736 --> 27:28.097
But he is optimistic.

27:28.296 --> 27:29.337
I guess

27:29.577 --> 27:31.137
he left the capital to relax.

27:31.496 --> 27:32.857
When he calms himself,

27:32.857 --> 27:33.817
he will return.

27:40.776 --> 27:42.456
Are you thinking about Suixue Pass?

27:43.417 --> 27:45.016
Commander Xiong Yisong died suddenly.

27:45.657 --> 27:47.417
It was said he was killed by a groom.

27:48.216 --> 27:50.417
But I always feel something is off.

27:51.097 --> 27:53.857
I'm afraid someone is behind it.

27:55.016 --> 27:56.577
And Li Duo has been steady and quiet.

27:56.657 --> 27:58.817
Unexpectedly, he recommended himself.

27:59.216 --> 28:02.016
I feel quite confused and uneasy.

28:03.216 --> 28:04.776
So, how do you plan to do?

28:05.776 --> 28:06.736
I have ordered Jin

28:06.897 --> 28:07.897
to travel day and night

28:08.496 --> 28:09.976
to Suixue Pass and investigate it.

28:11.496 --> 28:13.296
I only hope this is all a false alarm.

28:14.137 --> 28:15.016
May the Suixue Pass

28:16.016 --> 28:17.296
be safe.

28:21.377 --> 28:24.296
Congratulations,
you're going to take office tomorrow.

28:24.776 --> 28:26.496
Thank you.

28:30.817 --> 28:31.976
Among the three of us,

28:32.056 --> 28:34.177
Zhuang is the most capable.

28:34.448 --> 28:36.857
A commoner, gifted in mathematics,
is exceptionally promoted

28:36.857 --> 28:38.776
to Vice Director
of the Ministry of Revenue.

28:38.776 --> 28:40.696
From now on,
you will have a bright future,

28:40.696 --> 28:41.496
rising to the top.

28:41.696 --> 28:42.496
Zhuang.

28:42.696 --> 28:43.456
I hope

28:43.456 --> 28:44.857
you will back me up.

28:44.937 --> 28:46.696
Stop making fun of me.

28:47.097 --> 28:49.072
If you were given a position,
would you take it?

28:49.657 --> 28:51.776
With my personality,
I'm not official material.

28:52.137 --> 28:54.536
It's better for me
to travel around freely.

28:55.337 --> 28:57.097
Now, Marquis Muyang is dead.

28:57.496 --> 28:58.817
Guo Jin has returned her power.

28:58.817 --> 29:00.657
And Lishan Mountain has been open again.

29:01.456 --> 29:02.897
Finally, I have no regrets now.

29:04.137 --> 29:05.817
I can finally live a good life.

29:15.097 --> 29:16.097
May we live well.

29:17.177 --> 29:17.696
Right,

29:17.857 --> 29:19.696
do you know any familiar brokers?

29:19.817 --> 29:21.097
I want to buy a house.

29:21.736 --> 29:24.496
Not a very big house,
with a two-courtyard layout

29:25.177 --> 29:26.536
and a good location.

29:26.897 --> 29:28.817
It's best to be near the market,

29:29.216 --> 29:30.897
with taverns and eateries nearby,

29:31.417 --> 29:33.177
so it's convenient for daily shopping.

29:37.536 --> 29:38.337
What?

29:39.177 --> 29:41.056
Why are you buying a house?

29:41.937 --> 29:43.897
Of course, to live in.

29:45.536 --> 29:46.456
- Strange.
- Strange.

29:47.417 --> 29:48.456
What's wrong?

29:48.456 --> 29:49.648
Didn't you always say

29:49.648 --> 29:51.657
that you would travel around
and never settle down?

29:51.657 --> 29:53.137
We just heard you.

29:54.536 --> 29:57.296
Are you going
to give up traveling freely?

29:57.657 --> 29:58.216
Well...

29:59.417 --> 30:02.097
Who exactly do you buy a house for?

30:06.377 --> 30:07.417
We understand.

30:09.097 --> 30:10.496
What do you understand?

30:10.976 --> 30:11.776
Zhuang.

30:12.177 --> 30:13.216
Have you

30:13.216 --> 30:15.377
ever heard of a lady
in the capital named Yusheng?

30:15.377 --> 30:16.696
Of course, I've heard of her.

30:16.857 --> 30:19.256
She is talented, beautiful, and kind.

30:20.177 --> 30:21.016
It's a pity

30:21.256 --> 30:23.897
that she took a fancy to a vagabond.

30:24.137 --> 30:25.456
But I heard

30:25.937 --> 30:28.617
that the vagabond suddenly changed

30:28.617 --> 30:29.736
and wanted to settle down.

30:29.736 --> 30:32.097
So, he has to buy a house, right?

30:32.256 --> 30:33.216
Alright, enough.

30:33.377 --> 30:34.617
Stop making fun of me.

30:34.696 --> 30:35.817
Are we drinking or not?

30:37.337 --> 30:37.897
Drink.

30:38.417 --> 30:39.216
This is

30:39.216 --> 30:40.056
to the future.

30:40.417 --> 30:41.296
May we live well.

30:42.256 --> 30:43.056
To the future.

30:43.696 --> 30:45.377
Feng Zhiyao has fled to the capital.

30:45.776 --> 30:47.216
We sent men to track him down,

30:47.296 --> 30:48.536
but he escaped every time.

30:49.216 --> 30:51.016
Han Mingxi should
still be at Suixue Pass,

30:51.016 --> 30:51.817
but

30:52.937 --> 30:53.897
he's gone missing.

30:54.536 --> 30:55.417
Ignore him.

30:56.897 --> 30:57.696
Your Highness,

30:57.937 --> 31:00.177
the Han brothers know a lot
about Suixue Pass,

31:00.857 --> 31:02.417
especially regarding Li Duo's identity.

31:02.417 --> 31:04.696
If Feng Zhiyao brings the news
to the capital,

31:05.216 --> 31:06.617
we might lose Suixue Pass.

31:08.937 --> 31:10.177
Tell me about military supplies

31:10.177 --> 31:11.016
for Suixue Pass.

31:11.817 --> 31:12.657
Your Highness,

31:13.056 --> 31:15.817
we have a standing elite infantry
of 30,000

31:15.937 --> 31:17.256
and 12,000 cavalrymen

31:17.256 --> 31:18.536
under control.

31:18.776 --> 31:19.617
In the armory,

31:19.736 --> 31:21.137
there are 5,000 heavy crossbows,

31:21.137 --> 31:23.016
and enough spears
and sword-and-shield sets.

31:23.256 --> 31:25.897
There are also over 8,000 warhorses.

31:28.456 --> 31:29.256
Enough.

31:32.736 --> 31:33.897
Your Highness means...

31:39.337 --> 31:40.496
These warhorses,

31:41.137 --> 31:41.976
soldiers,

31:42.657 --> 31:43.817
plus us,

31:44.617 --> 31:46.776
are enough to break through the gate
of the capital?

31:49.417 --> 31:53.016
Your Highness, do you mean to rebel now?

31:55.897 --> 31:57.337
To achieve great things,

31:58.296 --> 31:59.216
the right time,

31:59.897 --> 32:00.657
right place,

32:01.216 --> 32:01.776
and right men

32:01.776 --> 32:02.937
are all indispensable.

32:04.377 --> 32:06.417
I have loyal, wise, and brave men

32:06.736 --> 32:08.377
like you all.

32:08.857 --> 32:10.016
You're all the right men.

32:10.897 --> 32:12.657
Suixue Pass stands
on the northern frontier.

32:12.657 --> 32:13.937
We can either march down

32:13.937 --> 32:15.216
or retreat behind the pass.

32:15.216 --> 32:15.937
That is

32:16.617 --> 32:17.417
the right place.

32:18.496 --> 32:19.296
Now,

32:20.577 --> 32:21.536
the news has leaked.

32:23.016 --> 32:24.897
This is a heaven-sent opportunity,

32:25.617 --> 32:27.736
the right time chosen by heaven.

32:30.016 --> 32:31.137
The time has come.

32:32.496 --> 32:34.337
It's time to give it our all.

32:40.216 --> 32:41.016
Your Highness,

32:41.216 --> 32:44.137
what should we do with Gao Wenhuan?

32:45.536 --> 32:46.337
Kill him.

32:49.937 --> 32:50.976
Since that day,

32:51.097 --> 32:52.937
Han Mingxi has never come back.

32:53.657 --> 32:55.976
That day, he said
he'd return at night and buy me drinks.

32:55.976 --> 32:57.736
However, he didn't come back.

32:58.536 --> 32:59.776
What about his things?

32:59.776 --> 33:00.377
They are

33:00.377 --> 33:01.256
all still here.

33:01.617 --> 33:02.617
Keep them safe.

33:03.137 --> 33:03.937
Go do your work.

33:04.296 --> 33:05.097
Yes.

33:19.577 --> 33:20.617
Little Li,

33:22.137 --> 33:24.137
how did Lishan Academy end up like this?

33:26.337 --> 33:27.776
Last time I saw you,

33:28.137 --> 33:29.577
you told me

33:29.736 --> 33:31.577
that Qingyun was healthy,

33:31.857 --> 33:33.536
writing books every day,

33:33.817 --> 33:35.937
and fishing and planting
in his free time, right?

33:38.177 --> 33:39.296
At that time,

33:40.097 --> 33:41.577
I indeed believed so.

33:43.577 --> 33:45.296
After they perished,

33:45.857 --> 33:46.937
I fell ill.

33:47.736 --> 33:48.577
Perhaps,

33:49.256 --> 33:51.577
to get through a hard time,

33:52.577 --> 33:54.817
I subconsciously hid all the truth

33:55.496 --> 33:58.296
and felt they were still with me,

33:58.817 --> 33:59.937
talking to me,

34:00.456 --> 34:01.536
eating with me,

34:01.937 --> 34:02.776
and working together,

34:03.456 --> 34:05.536
as if nothing had ever happened.

34:06.337 --> 34:07.377
All these years,

34:08.176 --> 34:10.777
you've endured it all by yourself.

34:11.136 --> 34:12.697
Until recently,

34:12.857 --> 34:14.496
Yao came up the mountain to find me

34:14.737 --> 34:16.056
and stayed by my side.

34:16.817 --> 34:18.897
Only then did I finally face it all.

34:24.136 --> 34:26.096
How could this happen?

34:28.176 --> 34:29.297
(Back then,)

34:29.737 --> 34:32.377
(it was I who begged your grandfather
to seal the mountain.)

34:33.136 --> 34:34.496
(The evidence of the fire)

34:34.777 --> 34:37.016
(at the Eastern Palace
pointed to Marquis Muyang.)

34:37.616 --> 34:40.752
(But Guo Jin made him the Chief Minister
of Imperial Court of Judicial Review.)

34:41.337 --> 34:43.096
(The evidence was instantly destroyed.)

34:43.496 --> 34:44.697
(The case took a turn,)

34:45.737 --> 34:47.777
(and Prince Ding's clan was
in a crisis.)

34:47.777 --> 34:49.897
(It was all to pave the way
for Guo Jin.)

34:50.897 --> 34:52.976
(She was malicious.)

34:53.056 --> 34:55.136
(How could she be allowed
to rule the state?)

34:55.737 --> 34:58.377
(But the court
was full of Marquis Muyang's men.)

34:58.857 --> 34:59.737
(Well,)

34:59.976 --> 35:01.536
(I had no other choice.)

35:05.697 --> 35:06.496
I understand.

35:07.417 --> 35:08.857
You don't need to blame yourself.

35:09.536 --> 35:11.817
Since my grandfather did it all

35:11.976 --> 35:13.496
by choice,

35:13.697 --> 35:14.937
nobody is to blame.

35:15.176 --> 35:18.616
Your grandfather cared about the nation
all his life.

35:19.056 --> 35:20.616
By sealing the mountain,

35:20.737 --> 35:23.777
he not only cut off Guo Jin's delusion
of holding the Fengshan ceremony

35:23.777 --> 35:26.777
but also aroused the response
of scholars nationwide.

35:28.777 --> 35:31.056
Unfortunately, a disaster struck.

35:31.536 --> 35:33.176
It's hard for me to take it.

35:33.897 --> 35:35.257
Even Master Helai

35:35.576 --> 35:36.897
couldn't cure them all.

35:37.976 --> 35:40.496
Back then, Lishan Academy had been
under siege for three years,

35:40.496 --> 35:41.737
lacking both food and medicine.

35:42.257 --> 35:45.056
Even if Master Helai
had the best medical skills,

35:45.377 --> 35:46.817
there was nothing he could do.

35:46.897 --> 35:47.857
Siege?

35:49.016 --> 35:51.016
Who dared to besiege Lishan Mountain?

35:52.176 --> 35:53.056
The Imperial Guard.

35:54.337 --> 35:56.257
They did so by the order
of the Empress Dowager.

35:56.976 --> 35:58.976
Lu Changfu led the troops to besiege us.

36:01.016 --> 36:01.817
Sir,

36:02.377 --> 36:03.737
it's all in the past.

36:10.456 --> 36:12.337
It is my fault.

36:13.656 --> 36:14.737
All these years,

36:15.056 --> 36:17.377
I've never considered the safety
of Lishan Mountain,

36:18.136 --> 36:19.616
causing such a great disaster.

36:20.777 --> 36:22.737
I cannot shirk my responsibility.

36:26.737 --> 36:28.176
After Prince Ding's crisis,

36:28.737 --> 36:30.176
you were still ill,

36:30.737 --> 36:32.737
yet you guarded the frontier
for six years

36:32.857 --> 36:34.297
until the frontier was stable.

36:35.176 --> 36:35.976
For this,

36:36.016 --> 36:37.297
you were bedridden.

36:38.976 --> 36:40.257
The integrity of Lishan Academy

36:40.616 --> 36:42.016
and my grandfather's choice

36:42.417 --> 36:44.697
have never been a burden to anyone.

36:45.777 --> 36:47.737
We have never resented you for a moment.

36:49.857 --> 36:51.176
Under siege,

36:52.217 --> 36:53.840
your calls for help went unanswered.

36:55.897 --> 36:57.496
I wanted to go down the mountain

36:58.136 --> 37:00.016
to seek help, but was forcefully stopped

37:00.337 --> 37:01.377
and locked up.

37:02.337 --> 37:03.817
By the time I broke open the room,

37:05.056 --> 37:06.496
they were already dead.

37:07.337 --> 37:09.056
They kept their promise

37:10.857 --> 37:13.297
at the cost of their lives.

37:14.136 --> 37:15.016
I feel truly sorry.

37:16.016 --> 37:16.976
Whatever we do

37:18.777 --> 37:20.737
cannot ease the pain.

37:21.616 --> 37:22.417
Yes.

37:22.777 --> 37:23.777
Gentlemen

37:24.576 --> 37:26.857
shouldn't have to prove their resolve
with their blood.

37:30.480 --> 37:33.040
(Back then, Lishan Academy had been
sealed for three years,)

37:33.040 --> 37:34.456
(lacking both food and medicine.)

37:34.832 --> 37:37.456
(Even if Master Helai
had the best medical skills,)

37:38.096 --> 37:39.536
(there was nothing he could do.)

37:40.080 --> 37:41.808
(I wanted to go down the mountain)

37:42.448 --> 37:44.272
(to seek help,
but was forcefully stopped)

37:44.560 --> 37:45.424
(and locked up.)

37:46.512 --> 37:47.984
(By the time I broke open the room,)

37:49.296 --> 37:50.640
(they were already dead.)

37:53.176 --> 37:53.976
Sir!

37:54.337 --> 37:55.337
What's wrong, sir?

37:55.697 --> 37:57.096
Sir?

37:57.737 --> 37:59.257
Are you having a heart attack?

37:59.616 --> 38:02.016
There's a clinic ahead.
Let's go get you checked.

38:03.176 --> 38:04.377
My illness

38:04.897 --> 38:06.176
cannot be cured.

38:08.337 --> 38:09.377
Let's go home.

38:23.440 --> 38:23.976
Whoa!

38:23.976 --> 38:24.937
Master Feng.

38:27.857 --> 38:28.737
Master Feng.

38:28.976 --> 38:29.857
Jin.

38:30.496 --> 38:31.576
What's wrong with you?

38:32.536 --> 38:33.937
I need to see His Highness.

38:35.056 --> 38:35.857
Okay.

38:36.337 --> 38:37.136
Okay.

38:38.656 --> 38:39.417
Get a physician!

38:39.417 --> 38:40.217
Yes.

38:41.616 --> 38:43.417
What happened? Who hurt you?

38:44.056 --> 38:46.377
Li Duo works

38:48.976 --> 38:50.616
for Mo Jingli.

38:57.777 --> 38:58.817
I didn't expect

38:59.016 --> 39:00.456
that Li Duo had been a spy

39:00.456 --> 39:02.616
right under your nose, Your Majesty.

39:03.176 --> 39:05.737
Mo Jingli, a despicable
and shameless traitor,

39:06.056 --> 39:07.737
actually faked his death to rebel!

39:09.096 --> 39:10.337
Calm down, Your Majesty.

39:10.456 --> 39:12.257
The military situation is urgent now

39:12.257 --> 39:14.377
and must be responded to in time.

39:17.656 --> 39:19.016
What is the situation now?

39:20.976 --> 39:21.777
Your Majesty,

39:22.456 --> 39:23.456
I've checked it.

39:24.096 --> 39:25.096
The rebels are cunning.

39:25.096 --> 39:27.417
They've won over some military officers
at Suixue Pass.

39:27.777 --> 39:28.616
Moreover,

39:28.777 --> 39:31.217
they took advantage of a shift
to secretly sneak in troops.

39:31.536 --> 39:32.737
Their vanguard has sneaked in

39:33.056 --> 39:34.857
and crossed the Heishui River.

39:35.257 --> 39:37.136
Their forces are marching
towards Luoxia Pass.

39:37.417 --> 39:39.096
Once they take Luoxia Pass,

39:39.417 --> 39:40.417
within ten days,

39:40.737 --> 39:41.937
the rebels

39:42.176 --> 39:44.257
will break open the capital.

39:44.417 --> 39:45.016
Then,

39:45.337 --> 39:46.656
what should we do?

39:47.937 --> 39:49.616
Opportunities in war are fleeting.

39:49.897 --> 39:52.432
We must dispatch troops immediately
for a head-on strike!

40:01.897 --> 40:04.377
Your Majesty, I request to go to battle.

40:04.777 --> 40:07.777
I wish to lead the troops
to crush the rebels

40:07.937 --> 40:09.297
to restore peace

40:09.496 --> 40:11.016
for the sake of Dachu.

40:11.536 --> 40:14.297
I swear not to return
until I defeat the rebels.

40:21.576 --> 40:22.377
Xiuyao.

40:23.257 --> 40:24.976
I shall entrust the peace of Dachu

40:25.616 --> 40:27.576
and the safety of the people

40:28.176 --> 40:29.857
to you.

40:32.944 --> 40:38.234
(Prince Ding's Mansion)

41:05.136 --> 41:05.897
Uncle.

41:25.576 --> 41:26.417
Come on.

41:27.777 --> 41:28.857
Let's go home.

41:33.245 --> 41:37.412
♪My life is full of ups and downs♪

41:39.472 --> 41:43.617
♪Every wound shows traces of love♪

41:44.240 --> 41:49.715
♪I've seen all the withering plants
in this world♪

41:50.192 --> 41:56.176
♪Until you went over the hills
to come close to me♪

41:57.393 --> 42:02.045
♪I saw your tender yet unwavering eyes♪

42:03.855 --> 42:08.247
♪Quietly full of joy and sorrow♪

42:09.072 --> 42:14.960
♪When it's over, I stand in the light♪

42:15.280 --> 42:19.920
♪In the reunion,
I comprehend the parting♪

42:20.944 --> 42:26.320
♪With half a lifetime of separation,
I send love to the distance♪

42:27.024 --> 42:33.023
♪As I travel through wind and frost,
I gaze at your figure♪

42:33.200 --> 42:38.471
♪You never forget me,
and I always miss you♪

42:39.499 --> 42:41.488
♪Until our hair turns gray♪

42:41.488 --> 42:44.144
(Preview)

42:45.176 --> 42:46.777
I will definitely come back safely.

42:47.937 --> 42:49.257
Then I wish Your Highness

42:49.857 --> 42:51.096
a triumphant battle.

42:51.817 --> 42:52.937
Are you crazy?

42:53.016 --> 42:53.976
My heart

42:54.016 --> 42:55.496
is wrenching.

42:56.056 --> 42:57.456
It aches so much.

42:57.536 --> 43:00.056
Has His Highness written to you lately?

43:00.496 --> 43:01.777
No, he hasn't for half a month.

43:02.297 --> 43:03.897
Rumors are spreading outside.

43:03.897 --> 43:05.536
Some say Luoxia Pass has been breached,

43:05.536 --> 43:07.937
and others say His Highness
has defected to the enemy.

43:14.736 --> 43:21.328
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

43:24.912 --> 43:31.056
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

43:33.264 --> 43:36.496
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

43:36.720 --> 43:42.736
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

43:43.056 --> 43:46.480
♪To the horizon's call♪

43:46.544 --> 43:53.104
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

43:54.160 --> 43:58.096
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

43:58.096 --> 44:03.792
♪Both joy and grief
make the trip worthwhile♪

